{"tid":1064062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家本土細路都係講蝗語","createTime":"2019-03-16T09:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T02:25:52.000Z","uid":201091,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b749465df04f6defb14e0a836419bb4c89abf6ff","tid":1064062,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:08:50.000Z","msg":"小弟今日落樓下打波<br />\n見到有班細路打緊<br />\n佢地開口埋口就係講蝗語<br />\n咁我以為佢地係支那人<br />\n點知突然彈咗一句<br />\n打手呀仆街<br />\n冇錯<br />\n佢地係用純正廣東話講<br />\n之後我先知原來成班細路<br />\n都識講廣東話<br />\n但係唔講<br />\n反而主要用蝗語黎溝通<br />\n我知道後<br />\n梗係立即扮上籃撞9佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又扮air ball 揼9佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後我想講香港究竟發生咩事<br />\n識講廣東話既唔講<br />\n反而係到講蝗話"},{"pid":"8ce8d5eb65bfeb6465ecee3b90fb3b5b80d4e26d","tid":1064062,"uid":228955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:27:29.000Z","msg":"好奇怪而家佢哋覺得講 蟲語 先至係威威"},{"pid":"2ee6cf5d6bf68d5cb8cac27238207ccde73c7512","tid":1064062,"uid":201091,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8ce8d5eb65bfeb6465ecee3b90fb3b5b80d4e26d","tid":1064062,"uid":228955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:27:29.000Z","msg":"好奇怪而家佢哋覺得講 蟲語 先至係威威"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:33:56.000Z","msg":"懷疑佢地係學校都係講蝗語"},{"pid":"72cd8c42fb64e07e5e847b86afd435997be2ed98","tid":1064062,"uid":200511,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"2ee6cf5d6bf68d5cb8cac27238207ccde73c7512","tid":1064062,"uid":201091,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8ce8d5eb65bfeb6465ecee3b90fb3b5b80d4e26d","tid":1064062,"uid":228955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:27:29.000Z","msg":"好奇怪而家佢哋覺得講 蟲語 先至係威威"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:33:56.000Z","msg":"懷疑佢地係學校都係講蝗語"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:35:26.000Z","msg":"普教中<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.g